{{Expand Vietnamese|Chùa Hoằng Phúc|date=April 2021}}{{Infobox building|image=HoangPhucPagoda5.jpg|image_size=|caption=弘福寺复原图|name=弘福寺|native_name={{lang-vi|Chùa Hoằng Phúc|link=no}}|native_name_lang=vi|former_names=敬天寺、知见庵等|alternate_names=|location=[[广平省|广平省]][[丽水县|丽水县]]顺泽村美水社|map_type=Vietnam|map_alt=|map_caption=位置|location_country=[[越南|越南]]|coordinates={{coord|17|11|57|N|106|48|50|E|region:VN|display=inline,title}}|address=|website=}}'''弘福寺'''（{{vie|v=Chùa Hoằng Phúc|hn=𫴶弘福}}）是一座位于[[越南|越南]][[广平省|广平省]][[丽水县|丽水县]]美水社的[[佛寺|佛寺]]。该寺处在越南的中北部海岸地区，始建于1300年，已有约700多年的历史，是越南中部最古老的佛寺之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://religion.vn/Plus.aspx/en/News/71/0/9028/0/6896/Quang_Binh_province_Reconstruction_of_main_facilities_of_Hoang_Phuc_pagoda_completed|title=Quang Binh province: Reconstruction of main facilities of Hoang Phuc pagoda completed|date=2016-01-12|accessdate=2016-01-18|publisher=religion.vn|archive-date=2016-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204232312/http://religion.vn/Plus.aspx/en/News/71/0/9028/0/6896/Quang_Binh_province_Reconstruction_of_main_facilities_of_Hoang_Phuc_pagoda_completed|dead-url=no}}</ref>在历史上曾历经多次重建及改名（曾用名如“知见庵”、“敬天寺”等）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Quang Binh province: Reconstruction of main facilities of Hoang Phuc pagoda completed|url=http://religion.vn/Plus.aspx/en/News/71/0/9028/0/6896/Quang_Binh_province_Reconstruction_of_main_facilities_of_Hoang_Phuc_pagoda_completed|accessdate=2016-01-18|date=2016-01-12|publisher=religion.vn|archive-date=2016-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204232312/http://religion.vn/Plus.aspx/en/News/71/0/9028/0/6896/Quang_Binh_province_Reconstruction_of_main_facilities_of_Hoang_Phuc_pagoda_completed}}</ref>
== 历史 ==
1301年，越南[[陳朝_(越南)|陈朝]]的皇帝[[陳仁宗|陈仁宗]]造访了这座寺庙，其后该寺被称为'''知见庵'''（Am Tri Kiến）。1716年，第六代阮氏[[廣南國|广南国]]领主[[阮福淍|阮福淍]]将这座寺庙改名为'''敬天寺'''（Kính Thiên Tự）。1821年，[[阮朝|阮朝]]的第二代君主[[明命帝|明命帝]]参观了该寺，并再一次将之改名为'''弘福寺'''（Hoằng Phúc Tự），现在常俗称为“chùa Trạm”或“Chùa Quan”。<ref name="Buddhist Shangha">{{cite web|title=Chùa Hoằng Phúc|url=http://m.phatgiao.org.vn/chua-viet/201412/Chua-Hoang-Phuc-Quang-Binh-16582/|access-date=2016-01-26|date=2014-12-12|publisher=Buddhist Shangha|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923090422/http://m.phatgiao.org.vn/chua-viet/201412/Chua-Hoang-Phuc-Quang-Binh-16582/|archive-date=2015-09-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>

该寺在历史上已曾多次重建。其于[[1985年|1985年]]间被热带[[熱帶氣旋|飓风]]所严重破坏，其后只剩下寺庙的大门和地基以及80公斤重的大钟和一些古佛像残存。<ref name="Buddhist Shangha2">{{cite web|title=Chùa Hoằng Phúc|url=http://m.phatgiao.org.vn/chua-viet/201412/Chua-Hoang-Phuc-Quang-Binh-16582/|access-date=2016-01-26|date=2014-12-12|publisher=Buddhist Shangha|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923090422/http://m.phatgiao.org.vn/chua-viet/201412/Chua-Hoang-Phuc-Quang-Binh-16582/|archive-date=2015-09-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>这之后，该寺则被列入了[[廣平省|广平省]]的文物名录。

自2014年12月起，佛寺的重建工作正式开始。<ref>{{cite web|title=Quảng Bình: Phục dựng, tôn tạo chùa Hoằng Phúc 700 năm tuổi|url=http://m.vtv.vn/trong-nuoc/quang-binh-phuc-dung-ton-tao-chua-hoang-phuc-700-nam-tuoi-20141202044858487.htm|accessdate=2014-12-20|publisher=VTV|language=vi}}</ref>2016年1月16日，[[柬埔寨僧王|柬埔寨僧王]][[狄旺|狄旺]]同[[越南政府|越南政府]]的官员和来自越南和缅甸的僧侣以及越南各地的佛教信徒参加了新寺的落成典礼。此后，弘福寺被认定为越南的国家历史遗迹。仪式当天，来自缅甸的佛教僧团曾将[[仰光大金寺|仰光大金塔]]的佛祖舍利供奉在了弘福寺的佛塔。<ref>{{cite web|title=Myanmar presents Lord Buddha's sarira to Vietnamese pagoda|url=http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/art-entertainment/150166/myanmar-presents-lord-buddha-s-sarira-to-vietnamese-pagoda.html|accessdate=2016-01-18|date=2016-01-16|publisher=VietnamNet|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126091605/http://english.vietnamnet.vn/fms/art-entertainment/150166/myanmar-presents-lord-buddha-s-sarira-to-vietnamese-pagoda.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cung nghinh xá lợi Phật tổ về chùa Hoằng Phúc tại Quảng Bình|url=http://www.vietnamplus.vn/cung-nghinh-xa-loi-phat-to-ve-chua-hoang-phuc-tai-quang-binh/366576.vnp|date=2016-01-15|publisher=Vietnamplus|language=vi|access-date=2022-04-02|archive-date=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714135335/https://www.vietnamplus.vn/cung-nghinh-xa-loi-phat-to-ve-chua-hoang-phuc-tai-quang-binh/366576.vnp}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cung nghinh xá lợi Phật tổ từ Myanmar về Quảng Bình|url=http://www.tienphong.vn/xa-hoi/cung-nghinh-xa-loi-phat-to-tu-myanmar-ve-quang-binh-959723.tpo|date=2016-01-15|publisher=Tiền Phong|language=vi|access-date=2022-04-02|archive-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613162145/http://www.tienphong.vn/xa-hoi/cung-nghinh-xa-loi-phat-to-tu-myanmar-ve-quang-binh-959723.tpo}}</ref>

